module.exports = Object.freeze({
    FORM_SIGN_UP_TITLE: "Sign Up",
    EMAIL_PLACEHOLDER: "Enter Email Address",
    PASSWORD_PLACEHOLDER: "Password",
    CONFIRM_PASSWORD_PLACEHOLDER: "Confirm Password",
    CREATE_ACCOUNT_BUTTON: "Create Account",
    EMAIL_ERROR: "Please enter a valid email",
    PASSWORD_ERROR: "Must have at least one capital letter, one numeric character, and one special character",
    CONFIRM_PASSWORD_ERROR: "Must be the same as the password",
    SUCCESS_MESSAGE: "Thank you! You have successfully submitted.",
    ACCOUNT_LINK: "Already have an account?",
    REQUIRED: "Required",
});
